<inglise> Whereas Article 9 (3) of Regulation (EEC) No 792/93 of 30 March 1993 establishing a cohesion financial instrument (3), amended by Regulation (EC) No 566/94 (4), provides that Article 23 of Regulation (EEC) No 4253/88 shall be applied mutatis mutandis; whereas, consequently, this Regulation covers the cohesion financial instrument; </inglise>
<eesti> n&otilde;ukogu 30. m&auml;rtsi 1993. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 792/93, millega asutatakse &uuml;htekuuluvuse rahastamisvahend, (3) (muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 566/94) (4), artikli 9 l&otilde;ikega 3 n&auml;hakse ette, et m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 4253/88 artiklit 23 kohaldatakse mutatis mutandis; j&auml;relikult h&otilde;lmab see m&auml;&auml;rus ka &uuml;htekuuluvuse rahastamisvahendit; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the rules set out in this Regulation should relate to all forms of financial intervention provided for in Regulation (EEC) No 4254/88 of 19 December 1988 laying down provisions for implementing Regulation (EEC) No 2052/88 as regards the European Regional Development Fund (5), as amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2083/93 (6), in Regulation (EEC) No 4255/88 of 19 December 1988 laying down provisions for implementing Regulation (EEC) No 2052/88 as regards the European Social Fund (7), amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2084/93 (8), in Regulation (EEC) No 4256/88 of 19 December 1988 laying down provisions for implementing Regulation (EEC) No 2052/88 as regards the EAGGF Guidance Sector (9), as amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2085/93 (10) in Regulation (EEC) No 2080/93 of 20 July 1993 laying down provisions for implementing Regulation (EEC) No 2052/88 as regards the financial instrument of fisheries guidance (11), as well as in Regulation (EEC) No 792/93; </inglise>
