<inglise> This information must be sufficiently detailed to allow the Commission to decide as soon as possible after consulting the authorities of the member States concerned, who shall bear the financial consequences in accordance with the third indent of Article 23 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 4253/88. </inglise>
