<inglise> Article 8 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 8 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The Commission shall maintain appropriate contacts with the Member States concerned for the purpose of supplementing the information supplied on the irregularities referred to in Article 3, on the procedures referred to in Article 5, and, in particular, on the possibility of recovery. </inglise>
